headline.main: Bridge Over I-64 to Be Named After Slain Virginia Trooper
headline.print_headline: Bridge Over I-64 to Be Named After Slain Virginia Trooper

lead_paragraph: A bridge in Newport News will be named after a Virginia trooper who was killed last year at a Richmond bus station.
